r%20pouting%20in%20a%20carseat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b521da955b01c3294d0716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon%20travels%20with%20her%20kids%20when%20her%20eldest%20was%20a%20toddler.%3Cp%3ETheBetterBeyond.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20told%20BI%20that%20taking%20the%20kids%20out%20for%20multiple%20activities%20in%20one%20day%20was%20a%20mistake%20when%20they%20were%20toddlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20typically%20do%20one%20thing%20successfully%20before%20things%20start%20to%20unravel%20and%20tantrums%20erupt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20school-aged%20kids%2C%20it's%20a%20mistake%20to%20pack%20your%20itinerary%2C%20she%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20child%20sits%20in%20a%20hammock%20on%20a%20bamboo%20balcony%20with%20green%20trees%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b5229cb4912df3ae1a1634%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon's%20eldest%20relaxes%20in%20a%20hammock%20in%20a%20treehouse%20accommodation.%3Cp%3ETheBetterBeyond.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20as%20her%20kids%20reached%20school%20age%2C%20planning%20more%20than%20one%20activity%20per%20day%20was%20easier%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20a%20mistake%20to%20pack%20the%20entire%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20nonstop%20itinerary%20without%20breaks%20100%25%20sucks%20the%20fun%20out%20of%20travel%2C%20and%20I%20am%20very%20good%20at%20accomplishing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BKids%2C%20like%20adults%2C%20need%20downtime%20to%20just%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20also%20added%20that%20long%20tours%20with%20school-aged%20kids%20are%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20I%20can%20find%20a%20short%20tour%20with%20an%20engaging%20guide%2C%20they%20are%20worth%20their%20weight%20in%20gold%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20teenagers%2C%20Cannon%20has%20forgotten%20to%20consider%20her%20kids'%20personal%20interests.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20images%3A%20Left%3A%20A%20boy%20sits%20smiling%20on%20a%20rocky%20cliff%20with%20the%20ocean%20in%20the%20background.%20Right%3A%20A%20person's%20legs%20are%20seen%20in%20a%20closed%20photo%20booth%20on%20a%20sidewalk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b51a63b4912df3ae1a1215%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon's%20son%20enjoys%20hiking%2C%20and%20her%20daughter%20likes%20visiting%20Instagram%20hot%20spots.%3Cp%3ETheBetterBeyond.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-teens-all-inclusive-spent-more-time-together-family-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraveling%20with%20teens%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20more%20challenging%20than%20with%20younger%20kids%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they%20have%20different%20interests%20and%20keeping%20them%20off%20their%20phones%20and%20engaged%20becomes%20a%20little%20harder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Cannon%20said%20she%20eventually%20realized%20that%20her%20son%20loves%20hiking%20and%20isn't%20into%20exploring%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20sometimes%20get%20frustrated%20because%20he%20seemed%20so%20indifferent%20in%20Paris%2C%20for%20example.%20He%20would%20take%20maybe%20five%20photos%20in%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20me%20ages%20to%20notice%20that%20he%20would%20take%2050%20photos%20on%20a%20hike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Cannon%20lets%20her%20kids%20plan%20a%20day%20of%20exploring%20during%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20interesting%20how%20differently%20the