ure%20documentaries%2C%20so%20he%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20how%20dangerous%20certain%20types%20of%20wildlife%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20hike%2C%20the%20guide%20encouraged%20us%20to%20touch%20the%20top%20of%20a%20leaf.%20Lucas%2C%20however%2C%20decided%20to%20also%20touch%20the%20underside%20and%20narrowly%20avoided%20a%20poisonous%20caterpillar%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20that%20moment%2C%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20didn't%20consider%20these%20environments%20'safe%2C'%20though%20we%20assumed%20he'd%20eventually%20get%20over%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tour%20in%20Ecuador%2C%20the%20family%20of%20four%20took%20trips%20to%20the%20Peruvian%20Amazon%20and%20the%20Costa%20Rican%20rainforest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20destinations%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20carefully%20avoided%20swarms%20of%20army%20ants%20on%20forest%20floors%20and%20bullet%20ants%20on%20handrails%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHis%20feelings%20never%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Lucas%20doesn't%20accompany%20the%20family%20on%20jungle%20or%20rainforest%20excursions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLucas%20still%20travels%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20to%20places%20with%20fewer%20creatures%20that%20can%20harm%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BElla%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20can't%20get%20enough%20of%20the%20jungle!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-when-traveling-with-babies-toddlers-kids-teens-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723757482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b61f845da406397bf47577%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-when-traveling-with-babies-toddlers-kids-teens-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tara%20Cannon%20has%20been%20traveling%20with%20her%20teen%2