2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Ffdic%5C%22%3EFDIC%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20CDs.%20With%20a%20CD%2C%20you%20know%20that%20your%20account%20balance%20is%20federally%20insured%20for%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20in%20individual%20bank%20accounts%20and%20%24500%2C000%20in%20joint%20bank%20accounts.%20Treasury%20bills%20are%20backed%20by%20the%20full%20faith%20of%20the%20U.S.%20government%2C%20though%2C%20so%20they%20are%20still%20low-risk%20and%20secure%2C%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20consider%20other%20types%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-fixed-income-investing%5C%22%3Efixed-income%20investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20assess%20risk%20tolerance%20to%20decide%20if%20another%20type%20of%20investment%20is%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20more%20focused%20on%20having%20access%20to%20your%20money%2C%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20can%20be%20another%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20erring%20on%20the%20side%20of%20caution.%20If%20you%20think%20that%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20cash%2C%20it's%20true%20that%20it%20may%20not%20earn%20as%20much%20in%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%2C%20but%20remember%2C%20in%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%2C%20you%20can%20get%20your%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Cheng.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20they%20have%20a%20variable%20interest%20rate%2C%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20allow%20you%20to%20deposit%20and%20withdraw%20money%20at%20any%20time.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ebest%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20still%20around%205%25%20APY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatured%20Nationally%20Available%20Deposit%20Rates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20bo