irit%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20choosing%20every%20extra%20amenity%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0such%20as%20snacks%2C%20WiFi%2C%20and%20extra%20legroom%20%E2%80%94%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%2C%20travelers%20will%20now%20have%20to%20pick%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.spirit.com%2FShared%2Fen-us%2FInfoPage%2FSPIRIT_Comparison_Grid_Web.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiers%20of%20extras%3C%2Fa%3E%20bundled%20together%2C%20with%20names%20such%20as%20Go%2C%20Go%20Savvy%2C%20Go%20Comfy%2C%20and%20Go%20Big.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20customers%20have%20already%20indicated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-airlines-says-flyers-spending-less-extras-like-food-baggage-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey're%20annoyed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20fees%20and%20aren't%20paying%20for%20extras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20flown%20Spirit%20or%20any%20low-cost%20carrier%20in%20the%20US%20before%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect.%20I%20now%20understand%20why%20Spirit%20is%20making%20this%20change%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20I%20suspect%20some%20passengers%20might%20not%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20is%20the%20largest%20ultra-low-cost%20carrier%20in%20North%20America%20and%20the%20seventh-largest%20passenger%20carrier%20overall%20in%20North%20America.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spirit%20Airlines%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd3b8ac9cf1420018d2eddb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpirit%20is%20known%20for%20its%20bright%20yellow%20planes.%3Cp%3EKen%20Wolter%2FShutterstock.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-ultra-low-cost-airlines-spirit-frontier-not-worth-it-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultra-low-cost%20carrier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20ULCC%2C%20is%20best%20described%20as%20offering%20a%20no-frills%20flying%20experience.%20Typically%2C%20everything%20costs%20extra%2C%20from%20a%20carry-on%20bag%20to%20picking%20your%20seat%20to%20refreshments%20on%20board.%20The%20seats%20can%20be%20thinner%20and%20usually%20do%20not%20have%20seatback%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20people%20may%20look%20down%20on%20ULCCs%20such%20as%20Spirit%20or%20Frontier%2C%20they%20are%20quite%20popular.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F12%2F20%2Fbudget-airlines-spirit-ryanair-how-they-make-money.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202023%2C%20budget%20airlines%20make%20up%20almost%20one-third%20of%20air%20traffic%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20Airlines%2C%20specifically%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Frebeccakhera%2Fspirit-airlines-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededicated%20fans%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20US.%20And%20even%20though%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-ticket-prices-cheaper-inflation-united-american-delta-junk-fees-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflights%20are%20actually%20getting%20cheaper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20perception%20has%20been%20the%20opposite.%20Why%3F%20Because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-raises-checked-bag-fees-joins-american-united-airlines-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eso-called%20junk%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fees%20that%20have%20been%20baked%20into%20Spirit's%20costs%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20airlines%20and%20raise%20profits%2C%20Spirit%20is%20introducing%20a%20tier%20system%20starting%20in%20mid-August.%20I%20took%20one%20of%20the%20last%20flights%20under%20the%20old%20system%20on%20July%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20took%20a%2024-hour%20trip%20to%20Disney%20World%20from%20New%20York%20City.%20To%20cut%20costs%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20fly%20Spirit%20for%20%24236%20round-trip.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gabbi%20at%203%3A13%20am%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20disney%20world%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb86c4955b01c3294e1bb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20to%20get%20up%20at%203%20a.m.%20to%20be%20at%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20on%20time.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20my%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20visiting%20Disney%20World%20for%20just%20one%20day%20for%20work%20%E2%80%94%20I%20only%20booked%20my%20trip%20a%20couple%20weeks%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-flights%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Flights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20other%20comparable%20itineraries%20(i.e.%2C%20leaving%20at%206%20a.m.%20and%20returning%20at%20some%20point%20after%208%20p.m.%20the%20same%20day)%20cost%20over%20%24300%2C%20at%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20routes%20that%20Spirit%20offers%2C%20though%2C%20can%20be%20as%20cheap%20as%20%2462%20from%20NYC%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20on%20July%2030%2C%20which%20is%20actually%20two%20weeks%20after%20I%20was%20%3Cem%3Esupposed%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20go.%20When%20I%20woke%20up%20on%20July%2016%20to%20get%20on%20my%206%20a.m.%20flight%2C%20I%20was%20greeted%20with%20the%20news%20that%20my%20flight%20was%20canceled%20due%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bair%20traffic%20control%20decision%20related%20to%20a%20weather%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20anticipating%20that%20rebooking%20my%20trip%20would%20be%20difficult%20and%20perhaps%20expensive.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20quite%20easy.%20Spirit%20refunded%20me%20for%20my%20canceled%20flight%20and%20my%20flight%20back%20home%20to%20NYC%2C%20which%20I%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20take.%20I%20also%20received%20a%20%24100%20voucher%20for%20the%20inconvenience.%20I%20then%20rebooked%20the%20same%20flights%2C%20just%20two%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Spirit%20terminal%20at%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20is%20Terminal%20A.%20It's%20the%20only%20airline%20at%20this%20terminal.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22back%20at%20laguardia%20in%20less%20than%2024%20hours%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3d36a5da406397bf402f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20still%20pitch-black%20when%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20moved%20to%20Terminal%20A%2C%20the%20Historic%20Marine%20Air%20Terminal%2C%20in%202022.%20An%20airline%20press%20release%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20convenient%20locations%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20I'd%20have%20to%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20parking%20lot%20was%20directly%20across%20the%20street%20from%20the%20terminal%2C%20which%20saved%20us%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20parking%20lot%20at%20laguardia%20terminal%20a%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3bdb35da406397bf3f6c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parking%20lot%20was%20surprisingly%20full%20for%20the%20hour.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20experience%2C%20I%20know%20that%20parking%20lots%20or%20garages%20can%20be%20a%20significant%20walk%20to%20the%20terminal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20prepared%20to%20give%20myself%20at%20least%2015%20minutes%20to%20get%20from%20my%20car%20to%20Terminal%20A%2C%20but%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20I%20could%20exit%20my%20car%20and%20be%20at%20the%20security%20line%20in%205%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20could%20also%20see%20the%20trademark%20bright-yellow%20planes%20queuing%20up%20on%20the%20tarmac.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20spirit%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb869c955b01c3294e1ba2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20yellow%20planes%20stuck%20out%20against%20the%20night%20sky.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20rebranded%20to%20the%20yellow-and-black%20planes%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20yellow%20makes%20the%20plane%20very%20distinctive%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20taxi%20cab%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20travel%20industry%20analyst%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Ftodayinthesky%2F2014%2F09%2F16%2Fspirit-picks-flamboyant-yellow-as-us-airlines-repaint-planes%2F15711597%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20could%20see%20a%20few%20classic%20New%20York%20taxis%20right%20next%20to%20the%20plane%2C%20I%20had%20to%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20terminal%2C%20I%20was%20guided%20by%20the%20bright-yellow%20signs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221932%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22spirit%20terminal%20at%20laguardia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb8582955b01c3294e1aab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221496%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20terminal%20was%20bustling.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20I%20turned%20I%20noticed%20Spirit's%20signs.%20One%20display%20was%20the%20typical%20spot%20where%20you%20can%20measure%20if%20your%20bags%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20heard%20a%20Spirit%20em