0eucalyptus%2C%20specifically%20the%20Sijo%20AiryWeight%20Eucalyptus%20sheets.%20It%20combines%20durability%2C%20softness%2C%20affordability%2C%20coolness%2C%20and%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sijo%20sheets%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669a845c49138fa6f6e3d66b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20comfy%20sheets%20that%20sleep%20cool%2C%20the%20Sijo%20AiryWeight%20Eucalyptus%20sheets%20are%20your%20best%20bet.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20flowed%20freely%20through%20the%20sheets%20as%20they%20wicked%20away%20moisture%20and%20heat.%20We%20also%20liked%20how%20cool-to-the-touch%20they%20were.%20Sets%20come%20in%2013%20colors%2C%20with%20or%20without%20top%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial-period%20language%20is%20just%20plain%20confusing.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20sheets%20for%20up%20to%20seven%20days%20and%20return%20them%20if%20they%20aren't%20for%20you.%20The%2030-day%20return%20period%20only%20applies%20to%20new%2C%20unused%20items.%20We%20also%20wish%20the%20sheets%20had%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%20for%20faster%20bed-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20when%20shopping%20for%20twin%20XL%20sheets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBed%20sheets%20are%20made%20of%20natural%20fibers%2C%20including%20linen%20and%20cotton%2C%20and%20synthetic%20materials%2C%20like%20polyester.%20We%20have%20a%20strong%20preference%20for%20the%20breathability%20of%20natural%20fibers.%C2%A0%20While%20cotton%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20option%2C%20there%20are%20vast%20differences%20in%20cost%2C%20look%2C%20and%20feel%20based%20on%20the%20type%20of%20cotton%20used.%20In%20this%20section%2C%20we%20will%20specifically%20focus%20on%20what%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20twin%20XL%20sheet%20set%2C%20but%20if%20you%20want%20more%20info%20about%20what%20to%20look%20for%2C%20see%20our%20main%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sheets%23what-to-look-for%5C%22%3Ebest%20bed%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20ill-fitting%20fitted%20sheet%20is%20frustrating%20and%20can%20even%20disturb%20your%20sleep.%20Most%20fitted%20sheets%20fit%20mattresses%20up%20to%2015%20inches%20thick%2C%20but%20if%20you%20think%20you%20might%20add%20a%20mattress%20topper%20or%20have%20an%20extra-thick%20bed%2C%20ensure%20you%20choose%20sheets%20with%20deep%20enough%20pockets%20to%20accommodate%20your%20setup.%20Twin%20size%20sheets%20will%20not%20fit%20on%20a%20twin%20XL%20bed%2C%20but%20twin%20XL%20sheets%20can%20fit%20on%20a%20twin%2C%20just%20with%20extra%20fabric.%20Sometimes%20retailers%2C%20like%20our%20Threshold%20pick%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPieces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20of%20our%20picks%20only%20come%20with%20a%20fitted%20sheet%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20buy%20pillowcases%20and%20a%20flat%20sheet%20separately%20(though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fis-a-top-sheet-necessary%5C%22%3Eyou%20don't%20need%20a%20flat%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E).%20So%2C%20pay%20attention%20to%20what%20pieces%20come%20with%20the%20sheet%20set%20to%20ensure%20you%20get%20what%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppearance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESheets%20come%20in%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20colors%20and%20patterns%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20look%20that%20doesn't%20fit%20your%20aesthetic.%20See%20what%20options%20are%20available%2C%20and%20pick%20a%20color%20that%20matches%20your%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20sheets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20specifically%20tried%20the%20twin%20XL%20sizes%20of%20the%20sheets%20in%20our%20guide%2C%20but%20they're%20all%20taken%20from%20our%20guides%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sheets%5C%22%3Ebest%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20are%20sheets%20that%20we've%20tested%20in%20other%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20we%20tested%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20wash%20and%20dry%20each%20set%20according%20to%20the%20instructions%20at%20least%20five%20times.%20That%20usually%20means%20washing%20the%20sheets%20in%20a%20cold%20cycle%20with%20gentle%20detergent%20and%20drying%20them%20on%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20sleep%20on%20each%20set%20for%20at%20least%20one%20week%20and%20note%20texture%2C%20comfort%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20coolness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3ENote%3A%20We%20also%20test%20for%20fit%20in%20our%20other%20sheet%20guides%2C%20but%20because%20the%20dimensions%20of%20the%20best%20twin%20XL%20sheet%20are%20different%2C%20the%20results%20don't%20apply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ETwin%20XL%20sheet%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20is%20a%20twin%20XL%20mattress%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETwin%20XL%20mattresses%20are%2080%20inches%20long%20and%2039%20inches%20wide.%20Twin%20XL%20mattresses%20comfortably%20fit%20a%20single%20sleeper%20up%20to%20six%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20tall.%20They%20are%20the%20same%20length%20as%20queen%20and%20king%20size%20mattresses.%20Many%20college%20dorms%20will%20use%20twin%20XL%20beds%3B%20they%20are%20also%20popular%20options%20for%20couples%20who%20want%20to%20create%20a%20split-king%20size%20bed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20want%20to%20double-check%20the%20measurements%20of%20your%20dorm%20bed%2C%20but%20most%20twin%20XL%20sheets%20are%2080%20by%2039%20inches%2C%20but%20the%20pocket%20depth%20can%20vary.%20If%20you%20bring%20a%20mattress%20topper%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20get%20sheets%20with%20roomier%20pockets%20to%20accommodate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20twin%20sheets%20fit%20a%20twin%20XL%20bed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20twin%20XL%20beds%20are%205%20inches%20longer%20than%20twin%20beds%20(80%20inches%20versus%2075).%20You%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20stretch%20twin%20sheets%20over%20the%20extra-long%20mattress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20twin%20and%20twin%20XL%20beds%20have%20the%20same%20width%2C%2039%20inches.%20While%20you%20could%20theoretically%20fit%20the%20best%20twin%20XL%20sheets%20on%20a%20regular%20twin%20bed%2C%20you'd%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20excess%20fabric%20to%20tuck%20under%20the%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20material%20for%20a%20twin%20XL%20sheet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20go%20wrong%20with%20cotton%20sheets.%20They're%20soft%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20clean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20a%20lighter%2C%20crisper%20feel%2C%20look%20for%20percale%20weaves.%20For%20denser%20sheets%20with%20a%20sheen%2C%20you%20may%20prefer%20sateen.%20Flannel%20sheets%20are%20made%20of%20cotton%20and%20are%20cozy%20and%20warm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20fabric%20options%2C%20we%20love%20linen%20sheets%20in%20warm%20weather.%20But%20they%20are%20pricey%20and%20wrinkle%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20jersey%20sheets%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20included%20jersey%20in%20our%20guide%20because%20we%20haven't%20thoroughly%20tested%20any.%20Because%20of%20the%20way%20it's%20knit%2C%20jersey%20tends%20to%20be%20less%20breathable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20your%20heart%20set%20on%20the%20T-shirt-like%20feel%20of%20jersey%2C%20we%20recommend%20looking%20for%20ones%20made%20of%20cotton%2C%20as%20that%20will%20give%20you%20a%20bit%20more%20airflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20thread%20count%20matter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThread%20count%20matters%20for%20cotton%20sheets%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20consider%20other%20factors%2C%20like%20the%20type%20of%20cotton.%20Think%20twice%20before%20simply%20buying%20the%20highest%20thread-count%20sheets.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20we%20spoke%20with%20said%20a%20good%20thread%20count%20is%20between%20300%20and%20400.%20However%2C%20you'll%20note%20that%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20L.L.Bean%20percale%20sheet%2C%20has%20a%20280%20thread%20count.%20These%20sheets%20are%20still%20fantastic%20because%20they're%20made%20with%20high-quality%2C%20extra-long-staple%20cotton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20Oeko-Tex%20certification%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oeko-tex.com%2Fen%2Four-standards%2Fstandard-100-by-oeko-tex%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStandard%20100%20by%20Oeko%20Tex%20certification%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20sheets%20have%20been%20independently%20tested%20for%20over%20100%20harmful%20chemical%20substances%20and%20are%20safe%20for%20human%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20L.L.Bean%20Percale%20Fitted%20Sheet%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20light%20blue%20L.L.%20bean%20pima%20cotton%20sheet%20and%20pillows%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f9317c34743a3001216b56e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20going%20through%20the%20wash%20many%20times%20over%20three%20months%2C%20the%20L.L.Bean%20Percale%20Fitted%20Sheets%20retained%20their%20soft%20feel%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20loose%20threads.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E100%25%20pima%20cotton%2C%20percale%20weave%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThread%20count%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E280%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%20(fitted%20sheet)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E39%26quot%3B%20x%2080%26quot%3B%20x%2015%