v%3EThe%20Kirkland%20Signature%20ice-cream%20bars%20were%20the%20clear%20winner.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20purple%20plate%20holding%20an%20ice-cream%20bar%20with%20a%20chocolate-flavored-and-nut%20coating%20on%20a%20gray%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ba28d1955b01c3294daf1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20definitely%20keeping%20the%20Kirkland%20Signature%20ice-cream%20bars%20in%20my%20freezer.%3Cp%3ETed%20Berg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20almonds%20turned%20off%20my%204-year-old%20entirely.%20My%206-year-old%20gave%20the%20Kirkland%20Signature%20bars%20an%20enthusiastic%20thumbs-up%20when%20he%20tried%20them%2C%20but%20ranked%20them%20last%20because%20he%20didn't%20like%20the%20almonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20my%20wife%20and%20me%2C%20these%20were%20the%20clear%20winners.%20The%20almonds%20added%20an%20extra%20crunch%20to%20the%20chocolate-flavored%20coating.%20However%2C%20these%20bars%20would've%20been%20the%20winner%20even%20without%20almonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchocolate-desserts-to-try-around-the-world-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E%20tasted%20milkier%20than%20the%20others%2C%20closer%20to%20candy-bar%20quality%2C%20and%20didn't%20crumble%20after%20a%20few%20bites.%20The%20ice%20cream%20was%20flavorful%20and%20wasn't%20heavy%20or%20icy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%204-year-old%20will%20probably%20love%20them%20once%20she's%20willing%20to%20try%20them%2C%20so%20I've%20made%20space%20for%20them%20in%20my%20freezer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-brand-of-ice-cream-bars-at-grocery-store-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723751617000%2