n-last-call-before-fatal-op%2Farticleshow%2F112552073.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Captain%20Deepak%20Singh%2C%2025%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20during%20a%20mission%20in%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Doda.%20He%20had%20lied%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20resting%2C%20while%20preparing%20for%20the%20mission.%20Commissioned%20in%202020%2C%20he%20was%20serving%20with%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20His%20family%2C%20preparing%20for%20his%20future%20wedding%2C%20mourns%20his%20loss%20but%20is%20proud%20of%20his%20sacrifice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22KALYAN%20DAS%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Foff-to-rest-captain-killed-in-doda-lied-to-mom-on-last-call-before-fatal-op%2Farticleshow%2F112552073.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hey%20influencers%20and%20brands%2C%20the%20FTC%20may%20come%20after%20you%20if%20buy%20fake%20followers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bunch%20of%20red%20social-media%20%26quot%3Blikes%26quot%3B%20fall%20from%20the%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be57241aa2ac29ee31a626%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJ%20Studios%2FGetty%20Images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FTC%20has%20a%20new%20rule%20saying%20creators%20can't%20buy%20fake%20followers%20on%20accounts%20they%20use%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20would%20crack%20down%20on%20false%20indicators%20of%20influence%20that%20could%20deceive%20consumers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrands%20also%20can't%20pay%20for%20fake%20engagement%20without%20risking%20the%20FTC's%20ire.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20been%20a%20bad%20look%20for%20influencers%20to%20buy%20fake%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarketers%20think%20you're%20phony%20and%20deceptive.%20Users%20wonder%20why%20there's%20a%20big%20gap%20between%20your%20audience%20size%20and%20%26quot%3Blikes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20the%20downsides%20of%20trying%20to%20buy%20influence%20are%20getting%20more%20severe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20or%20FTC%2C%20this%20week%20finalized%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fftc_gov%2Fpdf%2Fr311003consumerreviewstestimonialsfinalrulefrn.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20codifies%20how%20it%20plans%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20creators%20or%20businesses%20that%20buy%20fake%20followers%2C%20views%2C%20and%20other%20false%20indicators%20of%20social%20prominence%20in%20order%20to%20misrepresent%20their%20%26quot%3Binfluence%20or%20importance%20for%20a%20commercial%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20if%20you%20buy%20followers%20or%20views%20to%20boost%20engagement%20on%20your%20account%20or%20sponsored%20post%2C%20the%20FTC%20may%20come%20for%20you.%20The%20agency%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20consumers%20against%20deceptive%20advertising%20and%20other%20practices%20that%20harm%20consumers%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2019%2F10%2Fdevumi-owner-ceo-settle-ftc-charges-they-sold-fake-indicators-social-media-influence-cosmetics-firm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20taken%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20alleged%20purveyors%20of%20fake%20followers%2C%20subscribers%2C%20views%2C%20and%20likes.%20Its%20new%20rule%20gives%20it%20a%20sturdier%20framework%20to%20go%20after%20bad%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20rule%20doesn't%20establish%20anything%20brand%20new%2C%20but%20it%20will%20provide%20a%20new%20enforcement%20mechanism%20for%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20monetary%20relief%20for%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20Katherine%20Armstrong%2C%20a%20former%20FTC%20attorney%20and%20current%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20national%20advertising%20division%20of%20BBB%20national%20programs%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20constitutes%20a%20fake%20follower%3F%20The%20FTC%20said%20it%20could%20be%20several%20different%20types%20of%20accounts%2C%20including%20a%20bot%2C%20a%20hijacked%20account%20from%20a%20real%20user%2C%20and%20an%20account%20set%20up%20to%20imitate%20a%20real%20person%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20influencers%20should%20avoid%20engaging%20with%20these%20types%20of%20accounts%2C%20brands%20need%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20too.%20A%20company%20that%20buys%20fake%20followers%20or%20likes%20to%20make%20its%20business%20seem%20more%20popular%20could%20also%20draw%20the%20ire%20of%20the%20FTC%2C%20said%20Robert%20Freund%2C%20an%20advertising%20and%20e-commerce%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20brand%20paid%20to%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20fake%20followers%20and%20then%20ran%20just%20an%20organic%20post%20on%20their%20Instagram%20page%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20content%20is%20still%20commercial%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20Freund%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20still%20be%20advertising%20even%20if%20there's%20not%20express%20ad%20spend%20behind%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20exception%20to%20the%20rule%20is%20a%20social-media%20user%20who%20buys%20fake%20followers%20but%20doesn't%20use%20their%20Instagram%20or%20TikTok%20account%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20just%20want%20to%20grow%20a%20personal%20brand%20because%20I%20like%20having%20social-media%20clout%20and%20it%20would%20be%20cool%20to%20show%20my%20friends%20that%20I%20have%20a%20million%20followers%20and%20then%20I%20go%20buy%20a%20million%2C%20it's%20not%20really%20a%20commercial%20purpose%20that%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission's%20going%20to%20get%20involved%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Freund%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you're%20terminally%20online%20and%20just%20want%20to%20appear%20popular%2C%20go%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-and-brands-ftc-says-you-cant-buy-fake-followers-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723751211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be574f5da406397bf65823%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-and-brands-ftc-says-you-cant-buy-fake-followers-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FTC%20issued%20a%20new%20rule%20saying%20creators%20and%20brands%20can't%20buy%20fake%20followers%20or%20engagement%20on%20accounts%20they%20use%20to%20make%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dwhateley%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-and-brands-ftc-says-you-cant-buy-fake-followers-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tim%20Walz's%20drunken%20driving%20arrest%3A%20What%20happened%20to%20Kamala%20Harris's%20vice%20presidential%20candidate%20in%201995%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723751019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112552063%2Cimgsize-787558.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftim-walzs-drunken-driving-arrest-what-happened-to-kamala-harriss-vice-presidential-candidate-in-1995%2Farticleshow%2F112552053.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112552053.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%201995%2C%20Tim%20Walz%20was%20arrested%20for%20drunken%20driving%20by%20Trooper%20Stephen%20Rasgorshek.%20Walz%2C%20then%20a%20teacher%2C%20proactively%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20his%20principal%20and%20resigned%20from%20e