22000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lina%20Khan%20(left)%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be3f8f955b01c3294efba5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarris%20hasn't%20revealed%20whether%20she%20plans%20to%20replace%20Khan%20as%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20FTC.%3Cp%3EReuters%2C%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHarris%20is%20facing%20opposing%20pressures%20from%20Dems%20about%20whether%20to%20replace%20the%20FTC%20chair%2C%20Lina%20Khan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20VP%20hasn't%20given%20much%20away%20about%20her%20views%20on%20Khan%20in%20an%20apparent%20attempt%20to%20balance%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHarris%20has%20room%20to%20loosen%20the%20FTC's%20regulatory%20agenda%2C%20but%20risks%20upsetting%20progressives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20is%20trying%20to%20project%20unity%2C%20disagreements%20about%20corporate%20power%20and%20regulation%20are%20threatening%20to%20expose%20cracks%20in%20the%20solid%20exterior.%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20faces%20opposing%20pressures%20from%20opposite%20wings%20of%20her%20party%20about%20whether%20to%20replace%20Lina%20Khan%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20putting%20the%20presidential%20candidate%20in%20a%20delicate%20and%20awkward%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20that%20would%20shape%20the%20Vice%20President's%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20William%20Kovacic%2C%20former%20FTC%20chair%20and%20current%20law%20professor%20at%20George%20Washington%20University.%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%2C%20in%20isolation%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20policy%20do%20I%20want%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20right%20now%2C%20it%20doesn't%20seem%20that%20anybody%20is%20quite%20sure%20of%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20appointed%20Khan%20as%20chair%20in%20June%20of%202021%2C%20she%20has%20taken%20on%20an%20ambitious%20antitrust%20agenda%2C%20relying%20on%20seemingly%20forgotten%20federal%20laws%20to%20reign%20in%20monopoly%20power%20and%20corporate%20mergers.%20Her%20actions%20have%20drawn%20the%20ire%20of%20some%20big%20names%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20namely%20billionaire%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-billionaires-investors-kamala-harris-mark-cuban-reid-hoffman-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocratic%20mega-donor%20Reid%20Hoffman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20economic%20progressives%20like%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20have%20praised%20Khan's%20stances.%20Harris%20finds%20herself%20stuck%20between%20the%20two%20camps%2C%20struggling%20to%20determine%20how%20to%20be%20at%20once%20a%20pro-business%20and%20sufficiently%20progressive%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20turned%20heads%20when%20he%20went%20on%20CNN%20at%20the%20end%20of%20July%20and%20said%20Khan%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msnbc.com%2Fopinion%2Fmsnbc-opinion%2Fkamala-harris-linkedin-reid-hoffman-ftc-chair-lina-khan-rcna163897%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bwaging%20war%20on%20American%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20would%20prefer%20that%20Harris%20replace%20her.%20Barry%20Diller%2C%20a%20media%20mogul%2C%20called%20Khan%20%26quot%3Ba%20dope%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20would%20advocate%20for%20her%20removal%20should%20Harris%20win%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhan's%20term%20as%20chair%20ends%20in%20September%2C%20though%20FTC%20rules%20stipulate%20that%20she%20will%20remain%20in%20her%20position%20until%20the%20president%20appoints%20and%20the%20Senate%20confirms%20someone%20else.%20The%20confirmation%20process%20is%20involved%20and%20lengthy%2C%20according%20to%20Kovacic%2C%20who%20experienced%20it%20firsthand.%20Though%20Biden%20will%20be%20in%20office%20when%20her%20term%20is%20up%2C%20Kovacic%20anticipates%20that%20he%20will%20take%20Harris'%20wishes%20into%20consideration%20when%20deciding%20whether%20to%20replace%20Khan.%20Presidents%20are%20not%20obligated%20to%20appoint%20a%20new%20chair%20within%20a%20certain%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20intuition%20would%20be%20that%2C%20just%20as%20a%20general%20protocol%2C%20the%20President%20in%20this%20circumstance%20would%20respect%20the%20prerogatives%20of%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20Kovacic%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnother%20approach%20the%20President%20could%20take%20would%20be%20to%20say%2C%20'I'm%20not%20going%20to%20fill%20the%20spot.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20act%20on%20this%2C%20because%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20FTC%20will%20remain%20the%20chair%20until%20her%20successor%20is%20qualified%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20act.%20And%20Kamala%2C%20it's%20all%20yours%20after%20you're%20sworn%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20much%20of%20her%20specific%20policy%20positions%2C%20Harris%20has%20remained%20relatively%20tight-lipped%20about%20her%20plans%20for%20Khan%20and%20has%20thus%20far%20avoided%20ruffling%20too%20many%20feathers.%20Kovacic%20anticipates%20that%20she%20might%20try%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-tech-issues-ai-big-tech-crypto-silicon-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20further%20into%20the%20center%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20mergers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20stay%20away%20from%20tempering%20the%20administration's%20stance%20on%20monopolization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20article%2C%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Harris%20plans%20to%20propose%20a%20federal%20ban%20on%20corporate%20price-gouging%20and%20give%20the%20FTC%20investigative%20authority%20into%20corporations%20that%20violate%20the%20rules%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20Friday.%20They%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20whether%20she%20would%20replace%20Khan%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20FTC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20by%20this%20point%2C%20the%20nominee%20would%20have%20made%20more%20specific%20policy%20proposals%2C%20because%20they%20would%20have%20had%20to%20in%20order%20to%20secure%20the%20support%20of%20various%20factions%20within%20their%20party's%20coalition%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanford%20Gordon%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20politics%20department%20at%20New%20York%20University.%20%26quot%3BHarris%20really%20hasn't%20had%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20vagueness%20likely%20stems%20from%20the%20awkwardness%20of%20her%20positioning%20%E2%80%94%20she%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-leaders-support-harris-musk-andreessen-support-trump-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20also%20trying%20to%20appeal%20to%20progressives.%20Harris%20is%20raking%20in%20money%20from%20venture%20capitalists%2C%20has%20appointed%20her%20brother-in-law%20and%20Uber%20executive%20as%20a%20campaign%20advisor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-homes-where-lives-with-husband-washington-dc-california-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20is%20a%20Bay%20Area%20native%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F08%2F03%2Fbusiness%2Fdealbook%2Fsaying-the-quiet-part-out-loud.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20grumble%20about%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20members%20of%20the%20business%20and%20tech%20community%20hope%20Harris%20will%20be%20open%20to%20restoring%20a%20more%20relaxed%20relationship%20between%20the%20FTC%20and%20big%20corporations.%20Yet%20that%20same%20belief%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notus.org%2F2024-election%2Fharris-trump-lina-khan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esource%20of%20concern%20for%20economic%20progressives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whom%20Kovacic%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BWarren%20faction%2C%26quot%3B%20referencing%20the%20Massachusetts%20senator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20Biden%2C%20Harris%20has%20more%20freedom%20to%20loosen%20the%20FTC's%20regulatory%20posture%2C%20Kovacic%20said.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20president%20promised%20Warren%20significant%20say%20over%20economic%20regulatory%20agency%20appointments%2C%20and%20he%20has%20stayed%20true%20to%20his%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20Biden's%20promise.%20That's%20not%20Harris'%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20Kovacic%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20Harris%20must%20assess%20her%20relationship%20to%20the%20Warren%20wing%20of%20the%20party.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20loyalty%20does%20she%20feel%20to%20them%3F%20How%20much%20does%20she%20believe%20she%20has%20to%20cater%20to%20their%20tastes%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20a%20harmonious%20political%20relationship%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20of%20progressive%20and%20consumer%20advocacy%20groups%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20in%20response%20to%20Hoffman%20and%20Diller's%20comments%20and%20urged%20her%20to%20keep%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20and%20Diller%20have%20since%20tempered%20their%20stances%2C%20but%20Harris%20still%20seems%20stuck%20between%20the%20risk%20of%20alienating%20donors%20and%20inflaming%20economic%20progressives%20in%20her%20party.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Freidhoffman%2Fstatus%2F1819468284602851446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hoffman%20said%20that%20he%20has%20never%20talked%20to%20Harris%20about%20Khan%20and%20will%20support%20her%20campaign%20regardless%20of%20her%20FTC%20appointments.%20Diller%20qualified%20his%20comments%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-07-31%2Fbusiness-moguls-urge-harris-to-dump-biden-s-ftc-chair-lina-khan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'she's%20a%20dope.'%20She%20isn't.%20She's%20smart%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20overreaches%20in%20disrupting%20sensible%20business%20combinations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20will%20likely%20continue%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20faint%2C%20almost%20invisible%20middle%20ground%20between%20the%20two%20wings%20of%20her%20party%20by%20deflecting%20specific%20questions%2C%20Gordon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20%5BHoffman%5D%20is%20going%20to%20get%20her%20on%20the%20record%2C%20in%20public%2C%20making%20any%20kind%20of%20commitment%20whatsoever%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20would%20be%20politically%20extremely%20in-astute%20of%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Hoffman's%20public%20comments%2C%20it%20also%20remains%20unclear%20what%20Silicon%20Valley%20thinks%20overall.%20The%20world%20of%20venture%20capitalists%20and%20tech%20billionaires%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-political-divide-twitter-elon-musk-kamala-harris-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20suffered%20partisan%20divides%20this%20election%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20that%20there%20may%20be%20varying%20opinions%20among%20Democrats%20in%20the%20area%20as%20well.%20Kovacic%20said%20that%20some%20tech%20companies%20likely%20approve%20of%20Khan%20precisely%20because%20she%20targets%20their%20nemeses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20Reid%20Hoffman%20has%20grabbed%20the%20headlines%2C%20but%20we%20also%20know%2C%20from%20our%20own%20work%2C%20that%20there's%20a%20diversity%20of%20opinion%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20among%20VCs%20and%20entrepreneurs%20who%20want%20to%20encourage%20innovation%20and%20fairness%20in%20the%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Taylor%20Jo%20Isenberg%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20at%20the%20Economic%20Security%20Project%2C%20a%20progressive%20non-profit%20focused%20on%20economic%20issues%20and%20anti-monopoly%20actio