on%26quot%3B%20series%20is%20gathering%20perspectives%20from%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20industry%20verticals%20and%20corporate%20roles%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20drivers%20of%20change%20in%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20worker%20well-being%2C%20and%20C-suite%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenon%20Chen%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20strategy%20and%20growth%20at%20Clear%20Capital%2C%20is%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20time%20looking%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20AI%20and%20worker%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20company%20provides%20technology%20solutions%20for%20valuing%20real%20estate.%20%26quot%3BClear%20Capital%20is%20really%20about%20helping%20people%20make%20good%20decisions%20on%20properties%20based%20on%20accurate%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Chen%20said.%20He%20leads%20Clear%20Capital's%20strategy%20and%20go-to-market%20team%20and%20manages%20product%20partnerships%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%2C%20Chen%20said%20that%20workers%20were%20understandably%20nervous%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20to%20take%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20participant%20in%20BI's%20Workforce%20Innovation%20board%2C%20he's%20hoping%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20to%20surface%20the%20positive%20outcomes%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20also%20be%20the%20thing%20that%20helps%20workers%20have%20a%20better%20work%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20they%20have%20the%20right%20tools%20they%20need%20to%20do%20their%20job%20really%20well%20and%20be%20efficient%20and%20then%20focus%20on%20the%20things%20that%20really%20need%20human%20expertise%2C%20the%20harder%20problems%20to%20solve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20topic%20of%20workforce%20innovation%20a%20priority%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20for%20a%20few%20different%20reasons.%20One%2C%20culture%20and%20people%20are%20extremely%20important%20to%20our%20business.%20We%20have%20a%20number%20of%20core%20values%20that%20put%20people%20at%20the%20center%20of%20what%20we%20do%2C%20and%20how%20we%20think%20about%20being%20successful%20is%20really%20all%20around%20this%20idea%20of%20finding%20ways%20to%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20around%20you%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20little%20things%20throughout%20the%20day%20that%20remove%20stress%20or%20large%20solutions%20for%20how%20we%20can%20take%20care%20of%20our%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20post-COVID-19%20remote%20environment%2C%20workforce%20innovation%20is%20so%20important%20because%20how%20do%20you%20maintain%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20your%20core%20values%20and%20culture%20as%20you're%20embracing%20efficiencies%20and%20new%20tools%20to%20innovate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20work%20in%20the%20real-estate%20sector.%20What%20workplace%20issues%20are%20specific%20to%20your%20vertical%20and%20business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbsolutely.%20We%20work%20with%20valuation%20professionals%3A%20These%20are%20real-estate%20brokers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20appraisers%20who%20have%20expertise%20in%20understanding%20what%20a%20home%20is%20worth%2C%20and%20the%20process%20of%20analyzing%20data%20to%20form%20a%20credible%20opinion%20of%20the%20value%20of%20a%20home%20in%20any%20location%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20use%20AI%2C%20as%20well%2C%20to%20create%20other%20ways%20of%20valuing%20properties%2C%20such%20as%20automated%20valuation%20models%20that%20use%20AI%20to%20predict%20the%20value.%20We%20have%20a%20number%20of%20automated%20tools%20that%20let%20you%20use%20computer%20vision%20and%20AI%20to%20scan%20the%20home%20and%20generate%20an%20accurate%20floor%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20certainly%20fears%20that%20go%20along%20with%20that.%20Is%20AI%2C%20while%20it%20might%20have%20some%20benefits%20to%20create%20more%20accuracy%2C%20consistency%2C%20and%20better%20data%2C%20going%20to%20replace%20professionals%3F%20And%20what's%20the%20interplay%20between%20what%20highly%20trained%20certified%20professionals%20with%20local-market%20understanding%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20%5Band%5D%20innovation%20going%20with%20AI%20and%20data%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20we%20bring%20workforces%20together%20with%20modern%20tools%20in%20a%20way%20that%20doesn't%20just%20replace%20people%20but%20provides%20a%20better%20end%20product%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20the%20industry's%20struggling%20with%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20some%20concrete%20examples%20of%20how%20you're%20integrating%20AI%20innovation%20into%20the%20workforce%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20acquired%20a%20company%20called%20CubiCasa%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20that%20has%20an%20automated-floor-plan%20app%20that%20anyone%20can%20use%20on%20their%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20no%20special%20training%20or%20equipment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20walk%20through%20a%20home%2C%20scan%20the%20home%2C%20and%20it%20generates%20an%20automated%20floor%20plan%20and%20all%20of%20the%20data%20associated%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20that%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20enhance%20the%20process%2C%20not%20necessarily%20replace%20people%20but%20put%20better%20tools%20into%20people's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20path%20where%20technology%20makes%20the%20process%20more%20consistent%20but%20also%20gives%20options%20to%20our%20clients%20who%20have%20different%20risk%20levels%20for%20what%20types%20of%20tools%20they%20need%20for%20a%20particular%20decision.%20It's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20knowing%20how%20to%20make%20those%20options%20available%20and%20also%20equip%20people%20with%20the%20right%20technology%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20leadership%20challenges%20AI%20companies%20are%20facing%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hear%20a%20lot%20of%20conversations%20that%20go%20to%20concerns%20around%20people's%20jobs%20being%20replaced%20or%20people's%20skill%20sets%20maybe%20not%20being%20as%20appreciated%20anymore%20if%20there's%20an%20AI%20equivalent%20available.%20One%20of%20the%20quotes%20I%20heard%20from%20the%20CTO%20of%20United%20Wholesale%20Mortgage%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20AI%20that%20replaces%20people%20but%20people%20who%20use%20AI%20that%20will%20replace%20people%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20binary%20conversation%3A%20Is%20AI%20going%20to%20replace%20people%20or%20not%20replace%20people%3F%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20very%20strong%20link%20between%20the%20idea%20of%20worker%20well-being%20and%20AI%20because%20whenever%20there's%20fear%20of%20a%20new%20technology%20that%20seems%20powerful%20enough%20to%20cause%20some%20disruption%2C%20that%20creates%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20fear%20and%20uncertainty%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20it%20could%20also%20be%20the%20thing%20that%20helps%20workers%20have%20a%20better%20work%20experience%20because%20they%20have%20the%20right%20tools%20they%20need%20to%20do%20their%20job%20really%20well%20and%20be%20efficient%20and%20then%20focus%20on%20the%20things%20that%20really%20need%20human%20expertise%2C%20the%20harder%20problems%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20what%20other%20ways%20is%20AI%20driving%20change%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I've%20been%20thinking%20about%20lately%20is%20the%20human%20element%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20AI%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20generative%20AI.%20I%20think%20it's%20activated%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20brain%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20With%20machine%20learning%20and%20big%20data%2C%20it's%20activated%20the%20logic%20center%20of%20our%20brain%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20making%20predictions%3B%20we're%20replacing%20statistics%20with%20supersmart%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20generative%20AI%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20some%20of%20the%20creative%20aspects%20of%20things%2C%20using%20it%20to%20generate%20imagery%20and%20writing.%20With%20that%2C%20we%20now%20have%20this%20opportunity%20to%20talk%20about%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20create%20music%20with%20this%2C%20if%20I%20can%20create%20these%20other%20things%2C%20how%20do%20I%20deal%20with%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%20thinking%20about%20this%20just%20as%20tools%20and%20products%20and%20tech%2C%20we%20could%20start%20having%20a%20more%20holistic%20conversation%20about%20how%20this%20actually%20impacts%20both%20our%20personal%20lives%20and%20the%20way%20we%20go%20about%20doing%20creative%20things%20and%20our%20business%20life%20and%20the%20products%20we%20create.%20I%20think%20there's%20room%20for%20both%20at%20the%20table%20for%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-real-estate-industry-can-use-ai-enhance-human-expertise-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723748152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b0f7ed393cd3c8629b4eb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-real-estate-industry-can-use-ai-enhance-human-expertise-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20strategy%20and%20growth%20at%20Clear%20Capital%20shares%20how%20innovative%20technology%20can%20drive%20a%20better%20work%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhood%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Hood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines