mediate%20action%20regarding%20the%20midnight%20mob%20attack%20and%20meet%20the%20students'%20demands%2C%20Ms%20Pal%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can't%20trust%20me%20for%20one%20hour%20then%20send%20me%20home%20also%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20fate%20of%20her%20predecessor%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20sent%20on%20a%20long%20leave%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20was%20furious%20over%20his%20new%20posting%20less%20than%2012%20hours%20after%20his%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20one%20hour%20to%20do%20some%20official%20work.%20You%20need%20to%20believe%20me%2C%20I%20won't%20go.%20You%20have%20to%20believe%20me.%20If%20you%20can't%20believe%20me%20then%20don't%20expect%20anything%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Suhrita%20Pal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhrita%20Pal%2C%20who%20was%20with%20the%20state%20government's%20health%20department%2C%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20after%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20resigned.%20He%20was%20appointed%20Principal%20of%20the%20city's%20top%20medical%20college%20-%20National%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20-%20the%20very%20day%20he%20resigned%20from%20RG%20Kar.%20Both%20appointments%20were%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20the%20government%20notification%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh's%20new%20posting%20remained%20a%20non-starter.%20Initially%20he%20got%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20Principal's%20room%20by%20the%20students%20of%20National%20Medical%20College%2C%20who%20went%20on%20a%20protest%20immediately%20after%20the%20announcement.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20go%20on%20a%20long%20leave%20by%20the%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20RG%20Kar%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20students'%20protest%20had%20continued%2C%20despite%20the%20court%20order%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20take%20over%20the%20rape-murder%20case%20of%20a%20%C2%A031-year-old%20doctor%20that%20has%20shocked%20the