the%20order%20of%20the%20CAS%2C%20the%20IOA%20continues%20to%20stand%20in%20full%20support%20of%20Phogat%20and%20is%20exploring%20further%20legal%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IOA%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20in%20its%20statement%20further%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20ensuring%20that%20Vinesh's%20case%20is%20heard.%20It%20will%20continue%20to%20advocate%20justice%20and%20fairness%20in%20sports%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20rights%20and%20dignity%20of%20athletes%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20sports%20fold%20are%20upheld%20at%20all%20times.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20continued%20support%20and%20understanding%20of%20our%20stakeholders%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20August%2014%20decision%2C%20which%20dismisses%20Vinesh's%20application%20to%20be%20awarded%20a%20shared%20silver%20medal%20women's%2050%20kg%20category%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%202024%2C%20has%20significant%20implications%20for%20her%20in%20particular%20and%20the%20sporting%20community%20at%20large%2C%26quot%3B%20IOA%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20total%20disqualification%20of%20an%20athlete%20on%20a%20marginal%20discrepancy%20of%20100%20grams%20mandates%20deeper%20examination%20and%20raises%20questions%20about%20ambiguous%20rules%20and%20their%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20marginal%20discrepancy%20of%20a%20100%20grams%20and%20the%20resultant%20consequences%20has%20profound%20impact%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20Vinesh's%20career%20but%20also%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20ambiguous%20rules%20and%20their%20interpretation%2C%26quot%3B%20IOA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IOA%20firmly%20believes%20that%20the%20total%20disqualification%20of%20an%20athlete%20for%20such%20a%20weight%20infraction%20on%20the%20second%20of%20two%20days%20warrants%20a%20deeper%20examination.%20Our%20legal%20representatives%20had%20duly%20brought%20this%20out%20in%20their%20submissions%20before%20the%20Sole%20Arbitrator%2C%26quot%3B%20IOA%20added%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20claimed%20that%20the%20incident%20revolving%20around%20Vinesh's%20case%20highlights%20the%20%26quot%3Binhumane%20regulations%26quot%3B%20that%20don't%20take%20into%20account%20the%20physiological%20and%20psychological%20stress%20athletes%20take%2C%20particularly%20female%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20involving%20Vinesh%20highlights%20the%20stringent%20and%2C%20arguably%2C%20inhumane%20regulations%20that%20fail%20to%20account%20for%20the%20physiological%20and%20psychological%20stresses%20athletes%2C%20particularly%20female%20athletes%2C%20undergo.%20It%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20for%20more%20equitable%20and%20reasonable%20standards%20that%20prioritize%20athletes'%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20IOA%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIOA%20extended%20full%20support%20to%20Vinesh%20and%20confirmed%20that%20further%20legal%20options%20are%20being%20explored%20to%20ensure%20Vinesh's%20case%20is%20heard%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20was%20set%20to%20face%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt%20of%20the%20United%20States%20for%20the%20gold%20medal%20on%20August%207.%20She%20was%20disqualified%20before%20the%20women's%2050kg%20final%20after%20exceeding%20the%2050kg%20weight%20limit%20before%20the%20final%20on%20August%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20weigh-in%2C%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100%20grams%20over%20the%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20disqualification%2C%20Vinesh%20appealed%20for%20the%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%2050kg%20weight%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%208%2C%20Vinesh%20penned%20an%20emotional%20to%20announce%20her%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20wrestling.%20%26quot%3BMaa%20kushti%20(wrestling)%20won%20against%20me%2C%20I%20lost.%20Forgive