nreasonably%20declined%2C%20the%20National%20Task%20Force%20on%20Mental%20Health%20and%20Wellbeing%20of%20Medical%20Students%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollaborative%20planning%20of%20duty%20hours%20by%20heads%20of%20departments%2C%20faculty%2C%20senior%20residents%20and%20residents%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20and%2C%20if%20there%20is%20an%20increased%20clinical%20workload%2C%20the%20hospital%20or%20medical%20college%20should%20hire%20more%20senior%20residents%20and%20medical%20officers%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20to%20recognise%20that%20postgraduates%20and%20interns%20primarily%20serve%20educational%20purposes%20rather%20than%20filling%20gaps%20in%20healthcare%20staffing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrict%20implementation%20of%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC)%20regulations%20on%20ragging%20is%20also%20mandatory%2C%20according%20to%20the%20taskforce%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20emphasised%20that%20medical%20colleges%20should%20have%20active%20anti-ragging%20cells%20with%20strict%20penalties%20for%20offenders%20to%20mitigate%20the%20stress%20induced%20by%20ragging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20colleges%20could%20consider%20granting%20a%2010-day%20vacation%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year%20to%20both%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20medical%20students%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis%2C%20the%20taskforce%20said%20and%20unsderscored%20that%20this%20would%20allow%20the%20medics%20to%20meet%20their%20family%20members%20that%20could%20foster%20bonding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20appropriate%20conditions%20such%20as%20comfortable%20rest%20areas%2C%20nutritious%20meals%20and%20hydration%20facilities%20for%20medics%20during%20duty%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospitals%20should%20provide%20regular%20breaks%20and%20ensure%20food%20availability%20in%20duty%20rooms%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taskforce%20also%20recommended%20a%20gatekeeper%20training%20programme%20in%20medical%20colleges%20aimed%20at%20establishing%20a%20proactive%20network%20for%20identifying%20at-risk%20individuals%20and%20connecting%20them%20with%20professional%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20programme%20will%20involve%20comprehensive%20training%20for%20participants%20to%20recognise%20warning%20signs%20and%20refer%20students%20to%20mental%20health%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20psychiatry%20departments%2C%20local%20protocols%20should%20be%20developed%20and%20the%20gatekeeper%20training%20programme%20initiated%20across%20the%20campus%2C%20involving%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20taskforce%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMental%20health%20education%20should%20be%20integrated%20into%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20curricula%20through%20lectures%2C%20workshops%20and%20seminars%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20the%20report%20and%20recommended%20that%20medical%20teachers%2C%20students%20and%20the%20administration%20should%20undergo%20regular%20training%20in%20mental%20health%20--%20either%20through%20periodic%20in-person%20sessions%20or%20online%20via%20the%20Swayam%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20training%20modules%20should%20cover%20mental%20health%2C%20stress%20management%2C%20building%20resilience%2C%20prevention%20of%20substance%20use%2C%20gatekeeper%20training%20and%20basic%20counselling%20techniques.%20Specific%20emphasis%20should%20be%20placed%20on%20handling%20confidentiality%20matters%20concerning%20individuals%20with%20mental%20illness%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20abolishing%20fees%20for%20repeating%20semesters%2C%20saying%20this%20would%20reduce%20economic%20burden%20and%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransparent%20and%20standardised%20grading%20systems%20and%20an%20independent%20appeals%20process%20are%20essential%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20evaluation%20and%20assessment%20methods%2C%20it%20said%20%26quot%3Ba%20fair%20and%20unbiased%20evaluation%20system%20is%20essential%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20that%20institutions%20could%20offer%20a%20mix%20of%20grading%20systems%20to%20reduce%20stress%20and%20promote%20a%20collaborative%20learning%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20force%20also%20recommended%20introducing%20supplementary%20exams%20to%20reduce%20academic%20pressure%20and%20anxiety%20and%20for%20providing%20a%20fairer%20assessment%20system%20and%20supporting%20student%20wellbeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suggested%20announcing%20exam%20results%20using%20roll%20numbers%20to%20enhance%20privacy%2C%20reduce%20stress%20and%20promote%20a%20fair%20academic%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpanding%20postgraduate%20medical%20seats%20addresses%20healthcare%20needs%2C%20enhances%20specialist%20care%20and%20reduces%20student%20migration%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taskforce%20also%20recommended%20abolishing%20seat-leaving%20fees%20or%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20who%20abandon%20their%20seats%20after%20admission%20should%20be%20prohibited%20from%20applying%20to%20medical%20colleges%20for%2024%20months%20from%20the%20date%20of%20leaving%2C%20it%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20medical%20colleges%20can%20fill%20the%20vacated%20seat%20in%20the%20same%20category%20(government%2Fmanagement%20seat)%20in%20the%20next%20calendar%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20a%20comprehensive%20orientation%20programme%20within%20four%20weeks%20for%20undergraduate%20students%20and%20two%20weeks%20for%20postgraduate%20students%20upon%20joining%20was%20essential%20for%20new%20entrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20programme%20should%20introduce%20students%20to%20the%20medical%20profession%2C%20campus%20resources%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20physical%2C%20mental%20and%20spiritual%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20and%20also%20recommended%20involving%20family%20members%20during%20the%20induction%20programme%20and%20periodically%2C%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year%2C%20reasoning%20that%20it%20would%20help%20them%20understand%20the%20expectations%20and%20stressors%20faced%20by%20medics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20understanding%20would%20enable%20families%20to%20provide%20effective%20support%20and%20enhance%20the%20ability%20of%20students%20to%20cope%20with%20academic%20and%20clinical%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImplementing%20a%2024%2F7%20support%20system%2C%20such%20as%20the%20TeleMANAS%20initiative%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20is%20advisable.%20Medical%20colleges%20should%20have%20plans%20for%20referral%2C%20evaluation%2C%20management%20and%20follow-up%20for%20students%20with%20mental%20illnesses.%20Confidential%2C%20accessible%20counselling%20services%20must%20be%20widely%20promoted.%20Medical%20colleges%20should%20consider%20appointing%20at%20least%20two%20counsellors%20for%20every%20500%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20colleges%20should%20provide%20free%20diagnostics%20and%20treatment%2C%20including%20medicines%2C%20for%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20issues%20within%20the%20campus%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taskforce%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20NMC%20should%20establish%20a%20national%20portal%20for%20grievance%20redress%2C%20enabling%20secure%20and%20efficient%20complaint%20handling%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723737720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fdoctor-generic_650x400_81520610288.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-medical-body-suggests-not-more-than-74-hours-work-week-for-medics-weekly-off-days-6345535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Excessive%20duty%20hours%20pose%20risks%20to%20the%20physical%20and%20mental