20believe%20me%2C%20I%20won't%20go.%20You%20have%20to%20believe%20me.%20If%20you%20can't%20believe%20me%20then%20don't%20expect%20anything%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20vandalism%20happened%20during%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%C2%A0trainee%20doctor%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20institution%20last%20week.%20Women%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20had%20organised%20a%20vigil%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bwomen%2C%20reclaim%20the%20night%26quot%3B%20on%20Wednesday.%20During%20the%20vigil%2C%20which%20began%20at%2011%20pm%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20people%20entered%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20went%20on%20a%20rampage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVehicles%20were%20attacked%2C%20public%20property%20was%20damaged%20and%20the%20police%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20a%20lathicharge%20as%20well%20as%20firing%20teargas%20shells%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%20The%20Kolkata%20Police%20said%2015%20policemen%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20police%20this%20morning%20released%20some%20photos%20of%20people%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20mob%20that%20vandalised%20the%20hospital%20and%20sought%20information%20about%20them.%20The%20photos%20were%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20suspected%20rioters%20were%20circled.%20The%20arrests%20were%20announced%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20nine%20arrested%20people%20have%20not%20been%20revealed%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20Anubhav%20Mondal%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20protests%20outside%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20said%20he%20was%20among%20those%20in%20the%20photographs%20circulated%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BOur%20protests%20will%20continue%20and%20get%20bigger.%20Whoever%20thinks%20they%20can%20instil%20fear%20in%20us%20will%20not%20succeed%2C%20we%20want%20justice%20at%20any%20cost.%20Our%20most%20important%20demand%20is%20a%20neutral%20investigation%20through%20a%20court-monitored%20process%2C%20and%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mondal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20claims%20were%20made%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20seminar%20hall%20where%20the%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20was%20also%20vandalised%20by%20the%20mob%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20said%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort%20had%20happened%20and%20warned%20people%20against%20spreading%20rumours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20also%20visited%20the%20hospital%20on%20Thursday%20and%20assured%20doctors%20and%20medical%20students%20that%20he%20was%20standing%20with%20them%20after%20they%20told%20him%20that%20they%20were%20feeling%20insecure%20after%20the%20killing%20and%20violence%2C%20and%20were%20feeling%20%26quot%3Btraumatised%20and%20terrorised%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20CBI%20team%2C%20which%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20met%20the%20family%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20killed.%20Her%20body%20was%20found%20last%20Friday%20and%20an%20autopsy%20report%2C%20which%20had%20put%20the%20time%20of%20death%20between%203%20and%205%20am%2C%20revealed%20that%20several%20injuries%20were%20inflicted%20on%20her%20before%20she%20was%20smothered%20to%20death.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20police%20had%20arrested%20a%20civic%20volunteer%2C%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%20The%20parents%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20have%20told%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20that%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20was%20found%20in%20her%20body%2C%20indicating%20that%20she%20was%20gang-raped.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723737180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fs63oc9h8_kolkata-hospital_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h