%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20not%20be%20defensive%20about%20what%20I%20was%20wearing%20or%20what%20the%20time%20was%20because%20none%20of%20that%20matters.%20What%20matters%20is%20that%20I%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20like%20me%20live%20in%20constant%20fear.%20And%20we%20have%20no%20energy%20left%20to%20report%20each%20and%20every%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20NCR%20streets%20are%20full%20of%20dogs%20at%20night.%20They%20start%20barking%20or%20following%20when%20you%20cross%20by%20their%20side.%20I'm%20less%20scared%20of%20them%20now.%20At%20least%20they%20stop%20when%20you%20stand%20or%20they%20have%20a%20fear%20of%20sticks.%20These%20men%20whom%20I%20came%20across%2C%20are%20not%20scared%20of%20anything!%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20another%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Harassment%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20I%20was%20waiting%20for%20my%20cab%20near%20DLF%20m%2C%20Sector%20-18%2C%20Noida.%20A%20bike%20crossed%20and%20the%20guy%20sitting%20at%20the%20back%20waved%20and%20asked%20'kya%20rate%20legi'.%20He%20didn't%20even%20stop%20and%20everything%20happened%20within%20a%20flick%20of%20seconds.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThankfully%2C%20I'm%20back%20at%20home%20safely%20rn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sonal%20Pateria%20(%40SonalPateria)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSonalPateria%2Fstatus%2F1823822189550071865%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Noida%20Police%20have%20responded%20via%20their%20official%20X%20account%2C%20stating%20that%20an%20investigation%20has%20been%20launched%20into%20the%20mall%20incident.%20The%20case%20has%20been%20assigned%20to%20the%20Assistant%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20with%20a%20special%20team%20and%20CCTV%20footage%20review%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pateria's%20post%20on%20X%20has%20received%20over%20four%20lakh%20views%20and%20a%20range%20of%20comments.%20Several%20users%20shared%20similar%20experiences%20in%20the%20comments%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20terrible.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20condition%20in%20a%20metro%20town%20where%20educated%20people%20live%2C%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20what's%20happening%20in%20more%20remote%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20deeply%20heartbreaking%20and%20shameful%20that%20we%2C%20as%20a%20society%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20protect%20our%20sisters.%20Such%20incidents%20highlight%20how%20far%20we%20still%20have%20to%20go%20in%20ensuring%20their%20safety%20and%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20user%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20so%20disturbing%2C%20we%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20no%20one%20goes%20through%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20tweet%2C%20Ms%20Pateria%20mentioned%20that%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20ACP%20Praveen%20Singh%2C%20who%20assured%20her%20that%20they%20were%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20%26quot%3BThough%20I%20believe%2C%20this%20issue%20is%20more%20of%20a%20cultural%20problem%20rather%20than%20law%20and%20order.%20Still%2C%20Noida%20Police%20took%20this%20case%20into%20their%20hands.%20Looking%20up%20for%20the%20action%20%26amp%3B%20updates%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723734180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F9hgcp5mo_sexual-harassment-generic-istock_625x300_26_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshocked-with-audacity-woman-shares-series-of-harassment-incidents-on-delhi-ncr-streets-within-a-single-month-6345233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%2C%20Ms%20Pateria%20detailed%20the%20first%20incident%20near%20DLF%20Mall%20