emony%20got%20over%2C%20social%20media%20started%20buzzing%20with%20indignant%20protests%20from%20Congress's%20leaders%20and%20supporters.%20The%20Defence%20ministry%2C%20which%20was%20organising%20the%20event%2C%20issued%20a%20clarification%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20stem%20the%20tide%20of%20criticism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtocol%20dictates%20that%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20who%20enjoys%20cabinet%20rank%2C%20is%20seated%20in%20the%20front%20row%20during%20ceremonial%20events.%20%C2%A0This%20year%2C%20that%20row%20was%20occupied%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20Union%20ministers%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20S%20Jaishankar%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20seated%20in%20the%20fifth%20row%2C%20behind%20Indian%20Olympic%20medalists.%20%C2%A0Star%20Indian%20shooters%20Manu%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20Singh%2C%20and%20hockey%20players%2C%20including%20Indian%20Captain%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20and%20goalkeeper%20PR%20Sreejesh%2C%20were%20seated%20ahead%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20ministry%20said%20the%20seating%20arrangement%20at%20ceremonial%20events%20follows%20a%20table%20of%20precedence%20and%20protocol.%20%26quot%3BThis%20year%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20honour%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20medal%20winners.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20some%20Union%20Ministers%20were%20also%20seated%20behind%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20medal%20winners%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explanation%20was%20shredded%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Defence%20Ministry's%20feeble%20explanation%20that%20it%20was%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Brespect%20for%20Olympians%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20cut%20much%20ice.%20While%20Olympians%20deserve%20every%20bit%20of%20respect%2C%20I%20wonder%20how%20Cabinet%20Ministers%20like%20Amit%20Shah%20or%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20ji%20get%20front%20row%20seats%20ahead%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20posted%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20protocol%2C%20the%20LoPs%20of%20both%20Houses%20must%20also%20be%20seated%20in%20the%20front%20row%2C%20but%20the%20seats%20for%20Rahul%20ji%20and%20INC%20President%20Shri%20Mallikarjun%20%40kharge%20ji%20were%20in%20the%205th%20row.%20This%20was%20not%20only%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20post%20of%20LoP%20or%20Rahul%20ji%3B%20it%20was%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20whose%20voice%20Rahul%20ji%20represents%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Venugopal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EModi%20ji%2C%20it's%20about%20time%20you%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20new%20reality%20post-June%204th.%20The%20arrogance%20with%20which%20you%20relegated%20Lok%20Sabha%20LoP%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20to%20the%20last%20rows%20during%20the%20Independence%20Day%20ceremony%20shows%20that%20you%20have%20not%20learned%20your%20lesson.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Defence%20Ministry's%20feeble...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFZYldFveTQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFZYldFveTQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20K%20C%20Venugopal%20(%40kcvenugopalmp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkcvenugopalmp%2Fstatus%2F1824045226551615552%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20foolish%20statement%20has%20come%20from%20the%20defence%20ministry%20that%20'this%20was%20done%20as%20we%20wanted%20to%20honour%20Olympians'.%20They%20should%20be%20honoured%20and%20so%20should%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20but%20did%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20J%20P%20Nadda%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20not%20wan