stigation%20against%20former%20prime%20minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20and%20nine%20others%20on%20charges%20of%20genocide%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20that%20took%20place%20from%20July%2015%20to%20August%205%20during%20the%20students'%20mass%20movement%20against%20her%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20was%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20the%20investigation%20agency%20of%20Bangladesh's%20International%20Crimes%20Tribunal%20against%20Ms%20Hasina%2C%20Awami%20League%20general%20secretary%20and%20former%20road%20transport%20and%20bridges%20minister%20Obaidul%20Quader%2C%20former%20home%20minister%20Asaduzzaman%20Khan%20Kamal%2C%20and%20several%20other%20prominent%20figures%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant's%20lawyer%20Gazi%20MH%20Tamim%20confirmed%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20tribunal%20started%20the%20probe%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%2076%2C%20fled%20to%20India%20on%20August%205%20after%20resigning%20from%20her%20post%20amidst%20unprecedented%20anti-government%20protests%20led%20by%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hasina-led%20Awami%20League%20along%20with%20its%20affiliated%20organisations%20is%20also%20named%20in%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20Bulbul%20Kabir%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Arif%20Ahmed%20Siam%2C%20a%20Class%20IX%20student%20who%20was%20killed%20during%20the%20anti-discrimination%20student%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(ICT-BD)%20investigation%20agency%20has%20started%20reviewing%20the%20charges...%20The%20accusation%20of%20genocide%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20has%20been%20recorded%20as%20a%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20accuses%20Ms%20Hasina%20and%20others%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20violent%20crackdown%20on%20student%20protesters%2C%20resulting%20in%20widespread%20casualties%20and%20human%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20progress%20of%20this%20investigation%20outcome%20would%20be%20communicated%20to%20the%20tribunal%20-%20originally%20constituted%20to%20try%20the%20Bengali-speaking%20hardened%20collaborators%20of%20Pakistani%20troops%20during%20the%201971%20Liberation%20War%20-%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20line%20with%20the%20tribunal%20law%2C%20reports%20published%20in%20various%20media%20from%20July%2016%20to%20August%206%20were%20submitted%20as%20necessary%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20a%20case%20of%20enforced%20disappearance%20was%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20against%20Ms%20Hasina%20and%20several%20others%2C%20including%20former%20ministers%20of%20her%20cabinet%2C%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20kidnapping%20a%20lawyer%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20Dhaka%20court%20on%20Thursday%20asked%20police%20to%20submit%20by%20September%2015%20the%20probe%20report%20of%20the%20case%20filed%20against%20Ms%20Hasina%20and%20six%20others%20over%20the%20death%20of%20grocery%20shop%20owner%20Abu%20Saeed%20in%20police%20firing%20in%20the%20capital's%20Mohammadpur%20area%20during%20the%20quota%20protests%20on%20July%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaka%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20Md%20Zaki%20Al%20Farabi%20set%20the%20date%20after%20the%20case%20was%20placed%20before%20his%20court%20for%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20coincided%20with%20the%20now%20scrapped%20National%20Mourning%20Day%20holiday%20marking%20the%20August%2015%2C%201975%2C%20assassination%20of%20Ms%20Hasina's%20father%20and%20Bangladesh's%20founder%20Bangabandhu%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20government%20of%20Nobel%20Laureate%20Professor%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20cancelled%20the%20holiday%20after%20discussions%20with%20different%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20some%20parties%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20keeping%20the%20mourning%20day%20holiday%20while%20others%20opposed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20previous%20years%2C%20no%20sombre%20wreath%20offering%20ceremony%20was%20held%20at%20Bangabandhu's%2032%20Dhanmandi%20private%20residence%2C%20later%20turned%20into%20a%20memorial%20museum%2C%20which%20was%20set%20ablaze%20by%20angry%20mobs%20after%20Ms%20Hasina%20resigned%20and%20fled%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20approves%20of%20it...%20but%20somebody's%20(Ms%20Hasina's%20regime)%20overdoing%20caused%20the%20overreaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20ex-premier%20Khaleda%20Zia's%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20leader%20and%20spokesman%20Amir%20Khasru%20Mahmud%20Chowdhury%20earlier%20told%20PTI%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'She%20Is%20Responsible'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20commentator%20and%20New%20Age%20newspaper%20editor%20Nurul%20Kabir%2C%20known%20for%20his%20stern%20criticism%20of%20the%20past%20regime%2C%20said%20Ms%20Hasina%20herself%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20defamation%20of%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kabir%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20can%20deny%20his%20contribution%20to%20Bangladesh's%20creation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20blame%20lies%20with%20them%20(Ms%20Hasina's%20regime%20or%20party)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20and%20witnesses%20said%20film%20actress%20Rokeya%20Prachi%20and%20several%20others%20tried%20to%20go%20to%20the%20museum%20to%20stage%20a%20sit-in%20but%20were%20dispersed%20by%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20group%20of%20stick-wielding%20people%20on%20Thursday%20positioned%20themselves%20in%20front%20of%20the%20museum%20to%20bar%20anyone%20from%20paying%20tributes%20in%20front%20of%20Mujibur%20Rahman's%20bust%20at%20Bangabandhu%20Bhaban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20pay%20my%20respects%20in%20the%20morning.%20But%20I%20could%20not%20place%20wreaths%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%201971%20veteran%20and%20leader%20of%20Krishak%20Sramik%20Awami%20League%2C%20a%20party%20belonging%20to%20the%20opposition%20camp.%20He%20complained%20that%20brickbats%20were%20thrown%20at%20his%20car%2C%20damaging%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student-led%20protests%20demanding%20reforms%20in%20government%20job%20quotas%20evolved%20into%20a%20government-toppling%20movement%20in%20early%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20230%20people%20died%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20incidents%20of%20violence%20that%20erupted%20across%20the%20country%20following%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Hasina%20government%20on%20August%205%2C%20taking%20the%20number%20of%20people%20killed%20to%20560%20during%20the%20three%20weeks%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Ms%20Hasina's%20resignation%2C%20a%20caretaker%20government%20led%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20was%20formed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20promising%20to%20address%20administrative%20and%20political%20reforms%20and%20hold%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20violence%20accountable%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723729440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fes5ieto_sheikh-hasina_625x300_11_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-tribunal-begins-genocide-probe-against-sheikh-hasina-9-others-6344639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh's%20International%20Crimes%20Tribunal%20has%20started%20an%20investigation%20against%20former%20PM%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20and%20nine%20others%20on%20charges%20of%20genocide%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20that%20took%20place%20from%20July%2015%20to%20August%205%20during%20the%20students'%20mass%20movement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwo