0including%20that%20of%20the%20premier%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20had%20said%20that%20the%20strike%20would%20go%20on.%20The%20resident%20doctors'%20association%20of%20Safdarjung%20Hospital%20had%20even%20gone%20on%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20associated%20with%20FORDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReversing%20its%20decision%20on%20Thursday%2C%20FORDA%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20anguished%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20violence%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20its%20earlier%20call%20had%20caused%20%26quot%3Bdistress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20FORDA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20recent%20troubling%20events%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20the%20Federation%20of%20Resident%20Doctors'%20Association%20(FORDA)%20addresses%20our%20colleagues%2C%20the%20medical%20community%2C%20and%20the%20public%20with%20renewed%20resolve...%20We%20acknowledge%20that%20our%20earlier%20decision%20to%20call%20off%20the%20strike%2C%20made%20in%20good%20faith%20based%20on%20assurances%20from%20the%20Ministry%2C%20has%20caused%20distress%20and%20disappointment%20within%20our%20community.%20We%20accept%20responsibility%20for%20this%20and%20understand%20the%20widespread%20discontent%20it%20has%20caused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20events%20that%20have%20unfolded%20since%2C%20particularly%20the%20violence%20last%20night%2C%20have%20shocked%20and%20anguished%20us%20all.%20This%20represents%20a%20dark%20chapter%20for%20our%20profession%2C%20We%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20and%20State%20Government%20for%20their%20failure%20to%20honour%20their%20commitments%20and%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%20during%20this%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20that%20it%20would%20resume%20the%20strike%20immediately%2C%20FORDA%20said%20it%20is%20developing%20a%20plan%20of%20action%20with%20other%20RDAs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20events%20of%20the%20past%20few%20days%20have%20reinforced%20our%20commitment%20to%20our%20rights%2C%20our%20dignity%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20our%20profession.%20This%20is%20a%20pivotal%20moment.%20We%20must%20stand%20firm%2C%20united%2C%20and%20resolute%20in%20our%20struggle%20for%20justice%20and%20the%20respect%20we%20deserve%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlack%20Badges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lucknow%20chapter%20of%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20association%20of%20doctors%20in%20the%20country%2C%20said%20its%20members%20will%20wear%20black%20badges%20on%20Friday%20to%20register%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20as%20well%20as%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20from%20the%20central%20government%20to%20make%20a%20stringent%20law%20for%20violence%20against%20doctors%20and%20hospital%20staff%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Every%20doctor's%20security%20under%20a%20safe%20environment%20should%20be%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20IMA%20Lucknow%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2016th%20August%202024%2C%20we%20will%20all%20wear%20black%20badges%20on%20duty%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20protest%20against%20such%20a%20brutal%20and%20heinous%20crime%20and%20to%20show%20solidarity%20towards%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERG%20Kar%20Attacked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20had%20organised%20a%20vigil%2C%20calling%20it%20'women%2C%20reclaim%20the%20night'%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20During%20the%20vigil%2C%20some%20people%20entered%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20we