D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Cops%20Find%20%26quot%3BIED-Like%20Material%26quot%3B%20After%20Terror%20Group%20Says%20It%20Planted%20Bombs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Police%20carried%20out%20searches%20in%20several%20places%20across%20the%20state%20on%20Independence%20Day%20after%20the%20banned%20terror%20group%20ULFA(I)%20claimed%20to%20have%20planted%20explosives%20in%20at%20least%2019%20places.%20Assam's%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20said%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20articles%26quot%3B%20were%20found%20in%20a%20few%20cities%20and%20towns%2C%20including%20Guwahati%2C%20and%20while%20they%20had%20circuits%20and%20batteries%2C%20there%20were%20no%20ignition%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20bomb%20threat%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20urged%20the%20terror%20group%20not%20to%20hurt%20Assam's%20development%20and%20resolve%20whatever%20issues%20they%20may%20have%20through%20dialogue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20began%20after%20ULFA(I)%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday%2C%20claiming%20that%20bombs%20had%20been%20planted%20in%2019%20places%20across%20Assam%20and%20that%20they%20couldn't%20be%20exploded%20because%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20error%26quot%3B.%20The%20group%20said%20it%20had%20planted%20the%20bombs%20to%20oppose%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Police%20carried%20out%20searches%20with%20dog%20and%20bomb%20disposal%20squads%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Sivasagar%20and%20several%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20Police%20GP%20Singh%20said%20suspicious%20articles%20were%20found%20and%20the%20material%20inside%20them%20has%20been%20sent%20for%20a%20forensic%20examination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssam%20Police%20has%20carried%20out%20extensive%20searches%20throughout%20the%20state%20today%20for%20explosive%20devices.%20At%20two%20places%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20suspicious%20articles%20were%20found%20which%20were%20opened%20by%20the%20Bomb%20Disposal%20Squad%20of%20Police.%20These%20articles%20do%20not%20have%20ignition%20devices%20inside%2C%20though%20some%20circuits%20and%20batteries%20are%20seen.%20The%20substance%20inside%20is%20being%20sent%20for%20forensic%2Fchemical%20examination%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAssam%20Police%20has%20carried%20out%20extensive%20searches%20throughout%20the%20State%20today%20for%20Explosive%20devices.%20At%20two%20places%20in%20Guwahati%20suspicious%20articles%20were%20found%20which%20were%20opened%20by%20Bomb%20Disposal%20Squad%20of%20Police.%20These%20articles%20do%20not%20have%20ignition%20device%20inside%20through%20some%20circuits%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20GP%20Singh%20(%40gpsinghips)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgpsinghips%2Fstatus%2F1824027727453663724%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilar%20articles%20have%20been%20seen%20at%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Sivasagar%2C%20Nalbari%20%26amp%3B%20Nagaon%2C%20which%20have%20been%20safely%20disposed%20of.%20In%20this%20connection%2C%20appropriate%20lawful%20investigation%20has%20been%20initiated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuwahati%20Police%20Commissioner%20Diganta%20Baruah%20said%20eight%20locations%20were%20searched%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20nothing%20was%20found%20in%20six%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20two%20places%2C%20we%20found%20materials%20that%20appear%20like%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%20(IEDs)%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20have%20any%20triggering%20mechanisms.%20A%20chemical%20analysis%20is%20being%20conducted%20of%20the%20material%20inside%20them%20to%20ascertain%20if%20it%20was%20an%20explosive%2C%26quot%