9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20her%20journey%20into%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F137498%2Fnortheast-india-abhineet-mishra-stereotype%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumour%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweta%2C%20now%2036%2C%20was%20born%20with%20spina%20bifida%20%E2%80%94%20a%20condition%20where%20the%20spine%20and%20spinal%20cord%20don%E2%80%99t%20develop%20properly%2C%20leaving%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20spine.%20Just%20before%20starting%20school%2C%20she%20underwent%20surgery%20and%20physiotherapy%2C%20which%20enabled%20her%20to%20walk%20using%20crutches.%20Women%20with%20this%20condition%20typically%20reach%20a%20height%20of%20about%204.6%20feet%2C%20shorter%20than%20the%20general%20average%20of%205.2%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20foray%20into%20comedy%20was%20initially%20inspired%20by%20her%20admiration%20for%20Indian%20comedians%20like%20Aditi%20Mittal%2C%20Azeem%20Banatwalla%20and%20Daniel%20Fernandes.%20She%20later%20explored%20the%20work%20of%20global%20comedians%2C%20such%20as%20Hannah%20Gadsby%2C%20Taylor%20Tomlinson%2C%20Ali%20Wong%2C%20and%20Jerry%20Seinfeld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sweta%20started%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99756%2Findias-stuttering-comedienne-pooja-vijay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echannelling%20her%20personal%20struggles%20as%20a%20disabled%20woman%20into%20comedy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20her%20purpose%20soon%20evolved.%20She%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20not%20only%20make%20jokes%20but%20also%20laugh%20at%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20few%20performances%20were%20downers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sweta%20first%20ventured%20into%20stand-up%20comedy%20in%202016%20in%20her%20hometown%20Pune%2C%20she%20noticed%20people%20often%20pulled%20back%20when%20they%20saw%20her%20on%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%20because%20people%20weren%E2%80%99t%20used%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20disabled%20woman%20doing%20comedy%3B%20it%20was%20a%20real%20downer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20has%20performed%20at%20over%20300%20open%20mics%20at%20different%20venues%2C%20including%20Boka%20Book%20Cafe%2C%20Vintage%20Comedy%20Club%2C%20Classic%20Rock%20Cafe%2C%20Space%20Comedy%20Club%2C%20Hippie%20at%20Heart%20and%20The%20Comedy%20Clubhouse%20in%20Pune%20and%20has%20been%20an%20advocate%20for%20disability%20inclusion%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sweta%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20not%20only%20make%20jokes%20but%20also%20laugh%20at%20themselves.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESweta%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20not%20only%20make%20jokes%20but%20